name: The Grid Game - Season Alpha - A3
description:
Hello, and welcome to The Grid Game, where everyone’s a winner!

This is not a chase. Every tile is its own work of art to be cherished and enjoyed.

After acquiring the first of two editions, contact @QuittersArts on twitter, or ‘quitters arts collective#3784’ on discord, for instructions.

16 Tiles.
3 Choices.
1 Rad Experiment.
